To start the game, ‘D’ has to be pressed at least twenty times to take off the aircraft.. 

 Pressing any other key will indicate a warning by giving a black flash.

 The controls for navigation are:

W - to move up

A - to move left    

S - to move down    

D - to move right

 To exit anytime the escape key has to be pressed twice. 

 Navigation of F16 within the view area is desired as outside the view area, it will 

be difficult to track the aircraft.

 To win the game the player must score more than 100 points.

 If the player runs out of fuel the game ends.

 High Scores are recorded at the end of the game and are displayed by pressing ‘H’ on the Game Menu.
